Description: This package provides a programmatic interface to an analysis-ready
    version of the nClimGrid Daily dataset created by NOAA and made available
    via AWS Open Data Registry.  It allows researchers to
    filter down the full nClimGrid dataset to their specific locations and
    times of interest. It pulls the data from an Amazon S3 bucket
    containing monthly parquet files (located at
    noaa-nclimgrid-daily-pds.s3.amazonaws.com/index.html#EpiNOAA) and
    makes it available for further processing in R.
